{
  "uuid": "7d4ce22c-e497-494c-a6f6-b1b8e37012b0",
  "name": "AI image summary generation",
  "summary": "**Conversation Overview**\n\nThe user requested help creating a simplified visual summary of a leadership content image. They asked Claude to analyze an image containing information about four leadership styles and create a condensed, visual version. Claude identified the content as covering four leadership styles (Executing, Influencing, Relationship Building, and Strategic Adaptation) and created an interactive HTML visualization with cards for each style, featuring icons, color coding, and hover effects. The user then requested two specific modifications: first, to arrange the layout in a balanced 2x2 grid format instead of the original flexible grid layout, and second, to change the title from \"4가지 리더십 스타일\" to \"강점기반 리더십 Framework\". Claude successfully implemented both changes, adjusting the CSS grid system to create equal-sized quadrants and updating the heading to emphasize the strengths-based leadership approach. The final deliverable was a clean, balanced visual framework displaying the four leadership domains in a structured 2x2 layout with responsive design for mobile devices.",
  "created_at": "2025-09-24T06:37:04.277543Z",
  "updated_at": "2025-09-24T06:41:52.689212Z",
  "account": {
    "uuid": "b56a29d3-1cd5-4b54-9081-30715f2a9d0a"
